{"tid":1390943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔，支援，義士，勇武，前線裝備用品 1","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:10:16.000Z","uid":289971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb94b08fb7f68e0470b4dad30c9e254d9c740f77","tid":1390943,"uid":289971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"你這班義士，手上什麼都沒有，怎樣玩呀<br />\n<br />\n照片的鐵欄，正常中間的鐵技，是空芯鐵通，好多地方都有，以後你們去到場地，馬上去找，找到後請用以下方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OO1v5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OO1v5f.png&h=da001d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手提電動磨機，做工程的人便知道，在照片鐵欄紅色點位，上下一鋸，馬上可以用，前後用膠紙包好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ky90MFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKy90MFB.png&h=175d7232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手鋸，在照片紅色點位，鋸鐵通上下鋸50％左右，把鐵欄放在地上，找一個肥仔企上去，鐵通便會斷開，如果多人，正常十五分鐘左右便可以分屍<br />\n<br />\n手鋸，鋸片，磨機，磨片，電池，全部分開多人拿去場地<br />\n明白便分享出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKAWj4v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKAWj4v.png&h=25e3d541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f511f2a840619c2b738539e6cb2341b2bf05d517","tid":1390943,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"囉機好危險㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5f62021e7a8d88828e327c4e2c38a71f1e5515","tid":1390943,"uid":289971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f511f2a840619c2b738539e6cb2341b2bf05d517","tid":1390943,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"囉機好危險㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"所以手鋸最安全"}]}